snippet.title: For Loop in PHP (IN 2 MINUTES) | Code Comet
snippet.description:
I show you how to write a for loop in php in 2 minutes! I give you what you need to know about for loops in php, along with an example.

For loops in php are exactly like any other for loop, it repeats code using a start and end.

Code Comet is a new series I'm starting to help people save time and frustration with coding. I'VE BEEN THERE, it's 2018... let's make code easier, and beautiful.

Want to learn how to code from scratch? Check out my video on How to Code for Beginners in 2018: https://youtu.be/woJb2hAfkO0
